My first commit for my [Home Assistant](https://www.home-assistant.io) config to a public Github repo.

https://github.com/simeonpashley/home-assistant_config

Hardware:

- [Rasberry Pi 3B](https://amzn.to/3bHxYIr)

Built on:

- [Home Assistant](https://www.home-assistant.io)
- [MQTT - Mosquitto](https://mosquitto.org)
- [Zigbee2mqtt](https://www.zigbee2mqtt.io)
- [Mariadb](https://mariadb.org)
- [ESPHome](https://esphome.io)
- [Node-RED](https://nodered.org) - more sophisticated automations
